&lt;h3&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Ascend&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;s9&quot;&gt;Backed by private equity from people-focused Alpine Investors, Ascend is building a modern platform for regional accounting firms that enables them to stay independent while accessing the resources of a large CPA firm to help them grow. Ascend provides access to growth capital, robust talent acquisition, best-of-breed technology, a catalytic leadership system, shared back-office services, and modernized equity incentives so that firms can surmount today’s industry challenges and reach their full potential. Founded in January 2023, the company attained revenues sufficient to qualify it as a Top 100 U.S. accounting firm within six months of operation. For more information, visit&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://caper-fuchsia-g45w.squarespace.com/&quot;&gt;ascendtogether.com&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;s9&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s8&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;GMP is a member of Ascend Partner Services, a PE-backed growth partner.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h3 class=&quot;s7&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s6&quot;&gt;About GMP Advisors&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;s9&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s8&quot;&gt;The &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.gmp-advisors.com/&quot;&gt;GMP &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;story began in 1982 when a group of seven professionals set out to create a better public accounting firm. Their goal was simple but ambitious: serve clients as trusted advocates for their businesses, their families, and their employees — while building a workplace free from micromanagement where professionals could flourish creatively, grow professionally, and maintain balance in their lives.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;s9&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s8&quot;&gt;More than four decades later, that founding vision still drives everything we do. Today, GMP Advisors is a full-service public accounting and advisory firm headquartered in Tyler, Texas, with more than 100 professionals across Audit, Tax, Advisory, and Outsourced Accounting/CFO services. We offer the depth and breadth of a large regional firm while preserving the collaborative, people-first culture our founders built from day one.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;s9&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s8&quot;&gt;We are in an active period of growth — expanding our team, deepening our service capabilities, and investing in the people who make it possible. If you’re looking for a place where your contributions are visible, your development is supported, and your career has real room to grow, GMP Advisors is that firm.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 class=&quot;s7&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s6&quot;&gt;The Role&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;s9&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s8&quot;&gt;GMP Advisors is seeking an &lt;strong&gt;Audit Manager &lt;/strong&gt;to join our growing Audit practice in Tyler, Texas. In this role, you will lead client engagements across a diverse portfolio that includes Oil &amp;amp; Gas, Construction, Government, and other industries — managing relationships, supervising and developing engagement teams, and delivering the high-quality work our clients have come to expect from GMP.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;s9&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s8&quot;&gt;This is a high-visibility position within a firm that is actively growing its Audit practice. For the right candidate, GMP offers meaningful career development and a clear path toward increasing responsibility over time.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
