&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Client Accounting &amp;amp; Advisory Services&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our Client Accounting &amp;amp; Advisory Services practice delivers the full spectrum of outsourced finance support — from Reactive Accounting (end to end general ledger accounting , AP, spend management, invoicing, payroll, and state/local tax reporting) to Proactive Accounting (cash flow management, budgeting, forecasting, Controller and CFO advisory, pre-acquisition diligence, and systems evaluation/implementation).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We serve clients through specialized teams across four industry verticals: Professional Services, Real Estate &amp;amp; Construction, Technology &amp;amp; Manufacturing, and High Net Worth Individuals (outsourced family office). Our team operates by a simple ethos — Curious, Humble, Honorable — and we&#39;re building toward a future where advisory work, not transactional accounting, defines how we serve clients.&lt;/p&gt;
