&lt;p&gt;In October 2023, GG Advisors made the strategic decision to join&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.ascendtogether.com/&quot;&gt;Ascend&lt;/a&gt; to usher in our next stage of growth. With Ascend’s partnership and shared resources – including technology, training and development – GG Advisors is well positioned for strong innovation and growth in the years to come.&lt;/p&gt;
